LYF Camp <%= @camp.year %> Registration Payment Confirmation

Thank you for registering for LYF Camp <%= @camp.year %>!
We have received your payment for the following <%= "camper".pluralize(@registrations.count) %>:

============================================================
<% @breakdown["campers"].each do |camper| %>
Camper Registration - <%= camper["name"] %>: <%= number_to_currency @breakdown["registration_fee"] %>
<% if @breakdown.key?("discount") %>
    <%= @breakdown["discount"]["description"] %>: - <%= number_to_currency @breakdown["discount"]["amount"] %>
<% elsif camper.key?("sibling_discount") %>
    Sibling Discount: - <%= number_to_currency camper["sibling_discount"] %>
<% end %>
<% if camper["extra_shirts_total"].to_i > 0 %>
    <%= "Extra Shirts (#{number_to_currency @breakdown["shirt_price"]} each) - #{camper["extra_shirts"]}" %>: <%= number_to_currency camper["extra_shirts_total"] %>
<% end %>
------------------------------------------------------------
<% end %>
<% if @breakdown["additional_donation"] %>
Additional Donation: <%= number_to_currency @breakdown["additional_donation"] %>
------------------------------------------------------------
<% end %>
Total: <%= number_to_currency @breakdown["total"] %>
============================================================

We are requiring all campers to be vaccinated for this year's camp.
Please email photo proof of each camper's vaccination status to lyf@tacl.org
by Saturday, July 24th.

We look forward to seeing you at camp!

============================================================

Registration Cancellation Policy: In this time of uncertainty, we want parents
to feel flexible and comfortable with their decision to send kids to camp. This
year, we will have a no-worry cancellation policy. Cancellations can be made up
until camp. If you have already paid for registration and would like to cancel,
we will apply 2021 registration fees to 2022 camp by default, and will issue
refunds upon request. To cancel your registration, please send an email with
your name and your camper's name to lyf@tacl.org.

